title: Cannot Transfer to EUNE
body:
Status: Transfer failed. You will be able to continue playing in the current region(.) Your account balance has not been debited. Your account has not been activated on the new region (.) 

Reason:Unexpected error () encountered during transfer. Please try again at a later date.

----------------------

I pasted above the error message I get when I try to do it. I have the RP required for the transfer but still it does not work.

What is causing this issue?

I am from the NE part of Europe, this account was transferred to Oceania when it was free, as a foolish mistake. But now I want to move it back to EUNE.

Regards!

replies.body:
Hey there,

You may wish to [contact player support](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) as they're the only ones who can assist with account specific inquiries.

Please note: Support responses may take 48 hours or more due to ticket backlog, please do not unnecessarily add information to your ticket (Unless in response to a support rep) or attempt to "bump" your ticket, as this may push you to the back of the queue.
